Arsene Wenger on Jack Wilshere: &quot;He needs these kinds of games to get back to his best level.&quot;<br />
<br />
Wenger on Wilshere not being included in the England squad: &quot;He could have been involved but if he keeps fitness maybe next time.&quot;

Arsene Wenger on Matt Macey: &quot;I think he took his chance very well. He is huge. He is quick. You do not often find that combination.&quot;<br />
<br />
Wenger on Macey: &quot;He is very agile too. He came very late to us. He came at 20 but he is intelligent and very focused.&quot;

Merson: &quot;If anyone is going to go to Man City &amp; win, believe it or not, it's Arsenal as they play a flamboyant way, they open the game up.&quot;<br />
<br />
Merson: &quot;If you are going to beat City, you have to have a go. There is no point sitting back and trying to nick something on the break.&quot;
